$(document).ready(function() {
    "use strict";

    if($('.glb-grid-24')){

        var cardId = '#ge-card-classificacao-93d9ca16-88b0-499c-80ce-f6be59edbe08',
                classificacaoFeedReady = false,
                classificacaoCardReady = false;

            $(document).on('bastian-feed-card_rendered', cardId, function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Feed Ready');
                classificacaoFeedReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

            $(document).on('card-classificacao-ready', function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Card Ready');
                classificacaoCardReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

        var initCardClassificacao = function(){
            if(classificacaoCardReady && classificacaoFeedReady){
                $('#ge-card-classificacao-93d9ca16-88b0-499c-80ce-f6be59edbe08').show();
            }
        }
    }

    try {

      var classificacao = new CardClassificacao({
        context: '#ge-card-classificacao-93d9ca16-88b0-499c-80ce-f6be59edbe08'
      });

      var classificacaoTracking = new CardClassificacaoTracking("93d9ca16-88b0-499c-80ce-f6be59edbe08");

    } catch (err) {}

});
</script></div><div class="areatemplate-esquerda

    var glb_realtime_map = {
        site: 'globoesporte',
        categories: ['home'],
        url: 'http://globoesporte.globo.com/rj/'
    };

    var realtime = function(realtimeLoaded, msg){
        if(realtimeLoaded){
            return;
        }

        $.getScript('http://s.glbimg.com/bu/rt/js/glb-rt.js', function(){
            $.ajax({
                dataType: 'jsonp',
                
                url: 'http://s.glbimg.com/es/ge/static/live/globoesporte/json/globoesporte-home-agregador.js',
                
                jsonpCallback: 'glbrealtime_callback',
                cache: true,
                success: function(json){
                    $.glbrealtime({
                        data: json,
                        debug: false
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    }

    var realtimeLoaded = false;

    $(window).on('load', function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "onLoad");
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    })

    setTimeout(function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "timeout")
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    }, 3000);

</script><link rel="stylesheet"

$(document).ready(function() {
    "use strict";

    if($('.glb-grid-24')){

        var cardId = '#ge-card-classificacao-d01387cf-12cf-480e-bad5-74a5d151b28f',
                classificacaoFeedReady = false,
                classificacaoCardReady = false;

            $(document).on('bastian-feed-card_rendered', cardId, function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Feed Ready');
                classificacaoFeedReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

            $(document).on('card-classificacao-ready', function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Card Ready');
                classificacaoCardReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

        var initCardClassificacao = function(){
            if(classificacaoCardReady && classificacaoFeedReady){
                $('#ge-card-classificacao-d01387cf-12cf-480e-bad5-74a5d151b28f').show();
            }
        }
    }

    try {

      var classificacao = new CardClassificacao({
        context: '#ge-card-classificacao-d01387cf-12cf-480e-bad5-74a5d151b28f'
      });

      var classificacaoTracking = new CardClassificacaoTracking("d01387cf-12cf-480e-bad5-74a5d151b28f");

    } catch (err) {}

});

(function($) {
    "use strict";

    $(document).ready(function(){
        cardElenco.init({
            urlInteratividadeNotas: "http://interatividade.globo.com:80",
            postUrlInteratividadeNotas: "http://post.interatividade.globo.com:80"
        });
    });

                        data: json,

                    });

            });
        });

        realtimeLoaded = true;

    (function (window, document) {
      var regexApp = function () {
        return /MobApp_Android|MobApp_iOS|MobApp_WP/;
      };

      var getUserAgent = function () {
        if (window.getUserAgent) {
          return window.getUserAgent();
        }
        return window.navigator.userAgent;
      };

      var extractAppFromUserAgent = function () {
        var appUserAgent, appVars, index, ua, userAgentParts;
        ua = getUserAgent();
        userAgentParts = ua.split(' ');
        for (index in userAgentParts) {
          appUserAgent = userAgentParts[index];
          if (regexApp().test(appUserAgent)) {
            appVars = appUserAgent.split('/');
            return {
              name: appVars[0].replace('_', ' '),
              version: appVars[1],
              frameworkVersion: appVars[2]
            };
          }
        }
        return null;
      };

      var addGlbOnAppClass = function () {
        var frameworkVersion, nativeAppInfo;
        nativeAppInfo = extractAppFromUserAgent();
        if (nativeAppInfo !== null) {
          if (nativeAppInfo.frameworkVersion) {
            frameworkVersion = parseInt(nativeAppInfo.frameworkVersion, 10);
            if (frameworkVersion >= 1) {
              document.documentElement.className += ' glb-on-app';
            }
          }
        }
      };

      addGlbOnAppClass(); // Garante que o header irá sumir rápido
    })(window, document);
  </script><header id="header-produto" class="header-navegacao header-home header-navegacao-ge" data-analytics="T"><div id="glbbarrawidget"></div><div class="floating-bar"><div class="header-bar"><div class="grid-12 clearfix area-principal row"><div class="column"><div class="menu-area to-left" data-analytics="S"><div class="menu-button"><div class="burger"><b></b><b></b><b></b></div><span class="menu-label">MENU</span></div><span class="menu-produto"></span></div><a class="logo-area" href="http://sportv.globo.com/site/"><h1 class="logo icon-produto">sportv</h1></a><div class="to-right"><div class="search-area"><form id="frmBuscaScroll" action="#"><input id="search-input-floating" type="text" name="q" placeholder="BUSCAR" class="search" /><label for="search-input-floating" class="glass-container"><div class="glass"><div class="iglass css3pie"></div></div></label></form></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="cube-container"><div class="cube"><div class="face front"><div class="grid-12 clearfix area-principal row"><div class="column"><div class="menu-area to-left" data-analytics="S"><div class="menu-button"><div class="burger"><b></b><b></b><b></b></div><span class="menu-label">MENU</span></div><span class="menu-produto"></span></div><a class="logo-area" href="http://sportv.globo.com/site/"><h1 class="logo icon-produto">sportv</h1></a><div class="to-right"><div class="search-area"><form id="frmBuscaScroll" action="#"><input id="search-input-top" type="text" name="q" placeholder="BUSCAR" class="search" /><label for="search-input-top" class="glass-container"><div class="glass"><div class="iglass css3pie"></div></div></label></form></div><div id="busca-padrao"></div><div class="banner"><div class="opec-area opec-right"><div class="opec-internal"><div id="banner_insert" class="tag-manager-publicidade-container"></div><script>typeof OAS_AD != "undefined" && OAS_AD("Right")</script

(function ($, window, undefined){
    "use strict";

    $(function () {
        var popinElement = $('[data-gui-popin=".mais-esportes-popin"]');

        var menuDestaque = $(".widget-menu-destaques");
        var widget = new WidgetMenuDestaques(menuDestaque, {
            quantidade: "16"
        });
        popinElement.on('appended.gui.gui-popin', function () {
            widget.bindSubitemClick();
        });
        widget.init();

        // Dropdown options
        // event trigger changes if we have touch support or not
        var activateEvent = 'click',
            enableOverlay = true;

        // for desktop
        if ($('html').hasClass('no-touch')) {
            activateEvent = 'hover';
            enableOverlay = false;
        }

        new GUI.Tab($('.gui-tab', menuDestaque));
        new GUI.Dropdown(popinElement, {
            activateEvent: activateEvent,
            enableOverlay: enableOverlay,
            mouseoverDelay: 400,
            boundToElement: '.widget-menu-destaques .gui-tab',
            position: "right" // no desktop. no mobile, center
        });
    });

}(jQuery, window));

        </td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-variacao"><div class="ge-card-classificacao-variacao"><span>${variacao}</span><span class="sprite-variacao sprite-${variacao_label}"></span></div></td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-pontos">${ pontos }</td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-vitorias">${ vitorias }</td><td class="ge-card-classificacao-col ge-card-classificacao-saldo">${ saldo_gols }</td></tr></script><script>
$(document).ready(function() {
    "use strict";

    if($('.glb-grid-24')){

        var cardId = '#ge-card-classificacao-c68192c5-b9a3-483b-a6cf-e163d3c2e9dc',
                classificacaoFeedReady = false,
                classificacaoCardReady = false;

            $(document).on('bastian-feed-card_rendered', cardId, function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Feed Ready');
                classificacaoFeedReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

            $(document).on('card-classificacao-ready', function() {
                console.debug('Classificacao: Card Ready');
                classificacaoCardReady = true;
                initCardClassificacao();
            });

        var initCardClassificacao = function(){
            if(classificacaoCardReady && classificacaoFeedReady){
                $('#ge-card-classificacao-c68192c5-b9a3-483b-a6cf-e163d3c2e9dc').show();
            }
        }
    }

    try {

      var classificacao = new CardClassificacao({
        context: '#ge-card-classificacao-c68192c5-b9a3-483b-a6cf-e163d3c2e9dc'
      });

      var classificacaoTracking = new CardClassificacaoTracking("c68192c5-b9a3-483b-a6cf-e163d3c2e9dc");

    } catch (err) {}

});

<script>
    (function (window, document) {
      var regexApp = function () {
        return /MobApp_Android|MobApp_iOS|MobApp_WP/;
      };

      var getUserAgent = function () {
        if (window.getUserAgent) {
          return window.getUserAgent();
        }
        return window.navigator.userAgent;
      };

      var extractAppFromUserAgent = function () {
        var appUserAgent, appVars, index, ua, userAgentParts;
        ua = getUserAgent();
        userAgentParts = ua.split(' ');
        for (index in userAgentParts) {
          appUserAgent = userAgentParts[index];
          if (regexApp().test(appUserAgent)) {
            appVars = appUserAgent.split('/');
            return {
              name: appVars[0].replace('_', ' '),
              version: appVars[1],
              frameworkVersion: appVars[2]
            };
          }
        }
        return null;
      };

      var addGlbOnAppClass = function () {
        var frameworkVersion, nativeAppInfo;
        nativeAppInfo = extractAppFromUserAgent();
        if (nativeAppInfo !== null) {
          if (nativeAppInfo.frameworkVersion) {
            frameworkVersion = parseInt(nativeAppInfo.frameworkVersion, 10);
            if (frameworkVersion >= 1) {
              document.documentElement.className += ' glb-on-app';
            }
          }
        }
      };

      addGlbOnAppClass(); // Garante que o header irá sumir rápido
    })(window, document);
  </script><header id="header-produto" class='header-navegacao header-editoria header-navegacao-ge' data-analytics="T"><div id="glbbarrawidget"></div><div class="floating-bar"><div class="header-bar"><div class="grid-12 clearfix area-principal row"><div class="column"><div class="menu-area to-left" data-analytics="S"><div class="menu-button"><div
